{
  "texts": [
    "The detection of AI-generated product reviews is an emerging challenge in natural language processing (NLP), particularly in the context of low-resource languages.",
    "As AI-generated text becomes increasingly sophisticated, distinguishing between humanwritten and machine-generated content is crucial for ensuring the authenticity of online reviews.",
    "In e-commerce platforms, product reviews play a pivotal role in shaping consumer trust, influencing purchasing decisions, and maintaining credibility between buyers and sellers.",
    "The proliferation of AI-generated reviews, however, poses a significant risk to the reliability of these platforms, making automated detection systems essential.",
    "While extensive research has been conducted on AI-generated text detection in English (Salminen et al., 2022; Luo et al., 2023), there remains a notable gap in studies focusing on particularly Malayalam language."
  ]
}